  <brief_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial of the Treatment of Mallet Fractures</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial of the Treatment of Mallet Fractures: Conservative Versus Operative Using One Meniscus Arrow®</official_title>
  <sponsors>
